>My problem is (I think) quite common: I have a '76 bus which has a
>malfunctioning heating system, it flows gas exhaust into the cab. In Italy
>we lack of information on good mechanics who can help me fix it - I don't
>know what to do and winter is freezing up here in Milan.
>
>I could try something myself but have poor information on how the system
>works and getting parts often means buying abroad at great cost.
>Also, my fair knowledge of specific english terms is not helping much
>searching list archives...
